{"tid":2022340,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"「抓教育，促洗腦」 - 李碧華","createTime":"2020-05-18T09:15:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-18T09:15:53.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"09710732c327edc1f017aa9dfbda1e887f737d26","tid":2022340,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T09:15:53.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200518/20919727/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200518%2F20919727%2F&d=pzZXWUTiTgu0UE2nVnCkCjH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=148ef3f8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200518%2F20919727%2F&h=0a73eb55\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200518/20919727/</a><br />\n<br />\n「抓教育，促洗腦」 - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200518/large/1589700188_a284.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200518%2Flarge%2F1589700188_a284.jpg&d=pzZXWUTiTgu0UE2nVnCkCjH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=747cbd33\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200518/large/1589700188_a284.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n教育界「文革2.0」明目張膽殺入香港，還由虛偽的教育局局長楊潤雄媚主操刀，真諷刺！楊偽局長子女均就讀國際學校，畢業後到澳洲留學，父親卻陰險地在港禍害人家的子女。<br />\n<br />\n關於今屆中學文憑試（DSE）歷史科必答題，問及「日本在1900至1945年間，為中國帶來的影響是否利多於弊？」本是open-ended問答。而教學中所有開放式問答是訓。。。。。。。。。。。。。追尋──這正是主子最忌憚的「思想自由」。各界已就試題遭紅媒及建制打手圍攻批鬥，提出抗辯理由，但教育局處心積慮，蘋果踢爆它早已插針考評局，對歷史科出題策略和內容知情，政治凌駕教育只是借機出手。<br />\n<br />\n文革摧毀文化歷史藝術教育&hellip;&hellip;殘害兩代人鮮活生命，複雜而狠毒之。。。。。。。。。。。。通識，鎮壓民主自由，培育顛倒是非指鹿為馬新一代。<br />\n<br />\n在文革2.0魔爪下，港人只能努力、團結、眾志成城：（一）九月時投票支持35+；（二）維護黃色經濟圈（衣食住行&hellip;&hellip;）；（三）支援獨立不屈揭露真相的《蘋果》，「贈閱券計劃」 <a href=\"https://hk.sports\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports&d=pzZXWUTiTgu0UE2nVnCkCjH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=661ebb5f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports</a>.appledail......XQHY3FDKW6HRMPTHLNU5ROJBI4/或「撐蘋果計劃」<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/l......TLMOUD3DUQLUJMJNXN22ZABM5Q/。珍惜目前僅有的自由！\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fl......TLMOUD3DUQLUJMJNXN22ZABM5Q%2F%E3%80%82%E7%8F%8D%E6%83%9C%E7%9B%AE%E5%89%8D%E5%83%85%E6%9C%89%E7%9A%84%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%EF%BC%81&d=pzZXWUTiTgu0UE2nVnCkCjH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=abafae82\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fl......TLMOUD3DUQLUJMJNXN22ZABM5Q%2F%E3%80%82%E7%8F%8D%E6%83%9C%E7%9B%AE%E5%89%8D%E5%83%85%E6%9C%89%E7%9A%84%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%EF%BC%81&h=4496286b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/l......TLMOUD3DUQLUJMJNXN22ZABM5Q/。珍惜目前僅有的自由！</a> <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"}]}